K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-1: aa mri ta ra sa ya na ta na dzha ya /
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-2: pra sha sta phra ma na shri kra na shasta ya na mo //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-4: tshangs pa la sogs pa drang srong dang /
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-7: mi'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-8: de nas tshangs pa'i gtso bo mchog /
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-9: dung gi thor tshugs khong seng can //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-10: tshangs pa kun grol chen po dang //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-11: drang srong chen po ljang sngon dang /
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-12: tsa ra ka dang nab so skyes //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-21: 'di kun 'khor dang bcas pa yis; ;kun bzang lha la phyag 'tshal nas //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-22: sman gyi dbang dang dam tshig mnos //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-24: de nas kun bzang bde gshegs kyis; ;sman gyi rgyal po bdud rtsi mchog /
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-25: nges pa'i lung 'di bka' stsal to //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299a-26: de nas thugs rje'i cho 'phrul gyis //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-0: sa rnams rab tu g-yos @299b nas ni; ;stong gsum 'jig rten sa steng du //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-1: thams cad sman chen ra sa yan //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-2: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-3: de ltar smin par byed pa yang //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-4: thugs rje rgya mtsho chen po las //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-5: thugs rje sprin ni khyab pa yis //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-6: sprin chen glog gi phreng ba can //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-10: chu yi phung po bdud rtsi yis //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-13: sa dang sman rnams kun gyi gsos //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-16: lcang lo can gyi 'khor kun du //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-18: chu de thams cad ro gcig ste //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-19: chu yi bcud la skyes pa ni //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-20: dpag bsam shing dang gel ba'i shing //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-21: ljon shing dang ni tsu ta'i shing //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-22: sa steng khebs par skyes pa ste //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-24: sdong po dang ni sdong chen dang //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-25: rtsa ba sdong bu shun lpags dang //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-26: snying po yal ga lo ma dang //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-28: de bzhin 'bru yi rnam grangs kun //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:299b-29: thams cad bangs shing smin par mdzad //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-2: so so'i yul dang gnas dag dang //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-3: mdog dang ro dang dri dang mthu //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-4: gang gis sa bon de nyid las //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-5: de dag rang rang 'byin par byed //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-6: de bzhin srog chags thams cad kun //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-7: ra sa ya na'i rdzas la spyod //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-9: bdud rtsi sgo ni rnam par phye //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-15: mi'i byang chub sems dpa'i dge bsnyen chen po dri
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-16: ma med par grags pa li tsa b'i la sogs
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-17: pa la bdud rtsi ra sa ya na ta nan
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-19: dang por bsgrub pa'i yul dang gnas ni /

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-22: gser mdog can gyi rtse mo rta rna ri zhes

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-28: tha ma nyi shu gcig gis 'grub //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-30: de dag kun gyi mtshan nyid ni //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300a-31: rtsa ba sdong bu yal ga dang //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300b-0: lo ma 'dab ma me @300b tag dang //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300b-5: 'di dag kun gyi yon tan yang //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300b-7: bdud bzhi nges par 'joms par byed //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300b-8: sman gyi rgyal po bdud rtsi'i mchog /
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300b-9: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal to //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300b-10: drang srong chen po 'di kun kyang //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300b-16: de yi dbus su sman gyi mchog /

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300b-18: ser skya ba las byung ba yi; ;'o ma bre gang btsags nang du //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300b-19: aa sho kanda'i phye ma dang //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300b-23: byin gyis brlabs pa'i sngags 'di dag /
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300b-24: stong ngam brgya ni rtsa brgyad bzlas //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300b-27: be la lig tsa na da lig sv'ah'a /

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:300b-33: nyi ma'i gung la bza' bar bya //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:301a-26: de kun rab tu bsal ba'i phyir //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:301a-27: phung po'i bdud dang nyon mongs bdud //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:301a-28: lha bu'i bdud dang 'chi bdag bcom //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:301a-29: bdud rtsi 'di yis sel bar byed //
K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:301a-30: shar lho nub byang gang yang rung //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:301b-21: srid pa chags nas srub shing gis //

K12D0841(1-8)-2_H0805-2:302b-2: ganda pri ya ku mah'a go na sig ham kha /
